quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Nagato, sortieing!
quotes.idle: What is it?
quotes.intro: I am the battleship, Nagato. I'll be counting on you. Leave the enemy battleships to me.
quotes.marriage: What is this...? I must be exhausted... What is this vision, deep inside my memories? Right, Admiral? Ships, both friend and foe... and then...  that massive light...
quotes.married: It'll be fine... I'm right here beside you.

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Mutsu, sortieing!
quotes.idle: What...?
quotes.intro: Second of the Nagato-class battleships, Mutsu. Pleased to meet you. Don't play with fire too much, okay? ...Please?
quotes.marriage: Admiral...! Why do you keep looking at my third turret? If you want to look, look over here♥
quotes.married: Since it's for you, dear, I'll do my best today as well, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Ise, setting forth!
quotes.idle: Yes, Admiral?
quotes.intro: Super-dreadnought, first of the Ise-class, Ise. Setting off!
quotes.marriage: Hey, Admiral, could we talk about the positioning of the fifth gun turret? Kuu... no good, huh... Eh? You don't get the meaning?
quotes.married: Hmm?

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Hyuuga, moving out.
quotes.idle: Hey... aren't you... Oh, it's you, Admiral.
quotes.intro: You're the admiral? I see. Anyway, second ship of the Ise class— Hyuuga. Remember me, if you would.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what's with that face...? You're getting all hot, too. Are you sick? Shall we lie down together?
quotes.married: Well, not bad.
quotes.remodel: Um, not bad... not necessarily good either though.

quotes.fleet_join: Yukikaze, always ready to sortie!
quotes.idle: Aye! I'll do my best!
quotes.intro: Kagerou-class destroyer, eighth ship, Yukikaze here! Please take good care of me!
quotes.marriage: I'm the Miracle Destroyer...? That's... it's not like that. I just... I always want to be at your side... Ah...! Th-That's not it, either!
quotes.married: It'll definitely be alright!

quotes.fleet_join: We mustn't be overconfident. Let's move forward with all our might!
quotes.idle: Um... Admiral? Is it mealti- no! Is it time to start the strategy meeting yet!?
quotes.intro: I'm the aircraft carrier, Akagi. If you're forming a carrier task force, just leave it to me.
quotes.marriage: Admiral... When I'm with you, I feel as though there is a way to change those fateful five minutes. I will do my best!
quotes.married: 1st CarDiv, Akagi, always ready to deploy! Admiral, please take a break sometimes.

quotes.fleet_join: I will not give this up.
quotes.idle: ...Umm... never mind. It was nothing.
quotes.intro: Aircraft Carrier, Kaga here. Are you my admiral...? I will place my trust in your abilities.
quotes.marriage: I'm... not good at expressing myself... That is... Admiral? I... Actually, you've made me very happy...
quotes.married: Well... I feel the same way.

quotes.fleet_join: My task fleet is now sortieing!
quotes.idle: Mmm... Nothing's going on. Well, I guess that's not a bad thing. It's a little boring, though... Time to go hang out with Hiryuu... ah, Admiral! Aye! Nothing to report!
quotes.intro: I'm the aircraft carrier, Souryuu. If you're making a carrier task fleet, you can count me in.
quotes.marriage: I'm... trying my hardest, you know? Am I being helpful? Hey... Admiral, what do I mean to you?
quotes.married: Admiral, can you spare some time go into town with me? There are things I'd like to get. Ah, not at all, not at all! I'll buy them myself. Really!

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! CarDiv 2, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Woah~ oh, oh, oh. So these are the blueprints for the revised Hiryuu-class aircraft carriers, the Unryuu-class. They sure were planning on making a lot... Wooow... this is amazing... A-Ah, Admiral, what was that? Sorry, but I wasn't really listening!
quotes.intro: Aircraft carrier Hiryuu here. Leave the carrier battles to me. I can fight on against any and all adversity.
quotes.marriage: Sometimes... I love it... That smile... Once in a while... It's okay to forget about the fighting, you know? Hey... look at me. Yeah!
quotes.married: Admiral, I appreciate the new planes, but I still prefer to fight alongside the Tomonaga Squadron. Eh? You'll grant my request? Thank you...! Ah...! I hugged you without thinking. Sorry♪

quotes.fleet_join: Shimakaze, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Oh!
quotes.intro: I'm destroyer Shimakaze. When it comes to speed, I'm the best there is— swift like the island breeze!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, did you watch me run? Well? I was fast, right? Right? Hmhmhm!
quotes.married: Eh? Admiral, you're tired from running? How slo~w...! But still, do your best!

quotes.fleet_join: I'll be the one to finish them off!
quotes.idle: Thanks for the hard work, Commander!
quotes.intro: Nice to meet you! I'm Fubuki! Thanks for having me!
quotes.marriage: Umm... hey... I... Commander, I mean... I l-l-lo... n-no... I have total faith in you! Sir!
quotes.married: I did it!

quotes.fleet_join: Everyone, let's do our best together.
quotes.idle: Thank you for the good work. Would you like some tea?
quotes.intro: I'm Shirayuki. Thanks for having me.
quotes.marriage: Being next to Commander's side, helping you out is my happiness. If only I can help and support you more..
quotes.married: I'm so happy...

quotes.fleet_join: Okay... I'll go!
quotes.idle: Good work.
quotes.intro: I'm... Hatsuyuki... nice to meet you.
quotes.marriage: Umm.. I…. l-like… I mean… erm… um…. never mind...
quotes.married: Thank you...

quotes.fleet_join: Yea~h! Let's go~!
quotes.idle: Good work! Commander!
quotes.intro: I'm Miyuki. Great to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Erm, umm… I like the commander!.. What is it? Don't look at me with that face!
quotes.married: Okay!

quotes.fleet_join: Nh...! I'm sortieing!
quotes.idle: You... Just how are long you planning on making me wait here!? What the hell! What are you thinking? Damn it... Hurry it up!
quotes.intro: So you're the commander, huh? Well, I expect you to work very hard.
quotes.marriage: I just wanted to tell you... Well, I don't really dislike you, you know. I guess... you can order me to do anything... you want... What are you...!? I-I didn't mean it like that!
quotes.married: Not bad.

quotes.fleet_join: Headin' out!
quotes.idle: Ah, yes... um... I'll do my best.
quotes.intro: U-um... my name is Isonami. Pleased to meet you.
quotes.marriage: Umm…. Admiral… do you have a girlfriend?.... Oh, so that's it. Fufu, hmm~ I see~♪
quotes.married: I'm very happy.

quotes.fleet_join: Ayanami, starting sortie!
quotes.idle: Yes, I'm all right?
quotes.intro: Nice to meet you. I'm Ayanami, a special class destroyer.
quotes.marriage: Am I Ayanami doing my best? Do I help you well? ...R-really! I'm so glad to hear it!
quotes.married: I did it!

quotes.fleet_join: Well, let go~! It's time for sortie!
quotes.idle: Nnn, you called?
quotes.intro: I'm Shikinami. I'll be in your care.
quotes.marriage: Commander, yeah, I've got something I wanna tell you, nah, it's not a complaint or anything, you know? Erm.. Umm… man, I can't say it!
quotes.married: Commander… It's not good to work so hard. … Hey, take your time!

quotes.fleet_join: Ooi, Torpedo Squadron, sortie.
quotes.idle: Will Kitakami-san be alright?..... I'm getting worried as I'm not with her... Hmm... I'm so worried... It's definitely, yes, there's definitely something that's about to happen! I have to go now!
quotes.intro: Hello. I'm Light Cruiser Ooi. Pleased to make your acquaintance.
quotes.marriage: Kitakami-san!... oh, it's the admiral? Ah, no, it's fine.. yes, I love the admiral too!
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened to the other girls, you say? Eh...? That's not it? Hmm, it's okay then.. It's okay...

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo squadron, headin' out!
quotes.idle: For some reason... My shoulder is all stiff, y'know— my shoulder. But I'm still so young, y'know~ I guess torpedoes are really kinda heavy, y'know~?
quotes.intro: I'm light cruiser Kitakami. Nice ta meet ya.
quotes.marriage: Eh...? You've taken an interest in me? Ya got good taste, y'know. Truly exceptional!
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened? Ya feelin' down? That's not like ya. Everything's fine!

quotes.fleet_join: Now it's our turn! Follow me! Everyone, form up behind me!
quotes.idle: Hi! Another splendid day today!
quotes.intro: It's the English-born returnee, Kongou, desu! Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... Even though it's the time and place... If you forget the mood and timing, it'll be a "no", you know?
quotes.married: Hey! Admiral! Even though you're always doing your best, I want you to not push yourself so hard, desu!

quotes.fleet_join: Off I go! With all my spirit! Held high!
quotes.idle: Ah, yes. Did you call for me?
quotes.intro: I'm Hiei, Kongou Onee-sama's sister. I'm looking forward to gaining experience and getting closer to my sister's brilliance.
quotes.marriage: Thank you for your favour, Commander... O-oh.. I see... I-I'm so embarrassed~! B-but... My heart... belongs to oneesama. Eh? It's not that kind of talk!?
quotes.married: Hiei can still fight some more. Commander, let's do our best together!

quotes.fleet_join: Haruna... is now... starting the sortie!
quotes.idle: Yes, I'm just fine.
quotes.intro: Fast battleship, Haruna, reporting for duty. You're the admiral, correct? I'm looking forward to working with you!
quotes.marriage: What's this...? I feel such an overwhelming desire to protect everyone... My comrades, and also... Admiral... You as well.
quotes.married: Admiral... I don't think I can ever repay you... for being this kind to me...

quotes.fleet_join: Sortieing! Now then, how shall we approach this?
quotes.idle: Your order, Commander.
quotes.intro: Is the mic's volume fine? Check. One. Two. ...Alright. Nice to meet you. I'm Kirishima.
quotes.marriage: If my predictions hold true, after the battle is over, ...No, it was nothing! I believe you and I are going to... most likely... most likely...♪
quotes.married: Your judgment is impeccable, as always.

quotes.fleet_join: Live combat...? I suppose it can't be helped.
quotes.idle: A pleasant breeze, isn't it?
quotes.intro: Aircraft carrier, Houshou here. Although I'm inexperienced, I look forward to your guidance.
quotes.marriage: Someday... Someday, just the two of us... I would like to enjoy a nice, relaxing cruise with you, okay?
quotes.married: Admiral, thanks as always for the hard work. When you can, please be sure to relax a little.

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Fusou, setting sail.
quotes.idle: Admiral, the weather is good today...
quotes.intro: Of the two Fusou-class super-dreadnought battleships, I am the elder sister, Fusou. Please take care of me and my younger sister Yamashiro.
quotes.marriage: My main cannons, aren't they wonderful? But specialising in firepower too much can lead to all kinds of problems... If it's Admiral, I'm sure you understand, right?
quotes.married: Admiral… If you work too hard, your body will get bad. Oh, me?...I...*sigh*

quotes.fleet_join: Fusou-class battleship Yamashiro, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Fusou nee-sama?
quotes.intro: Of the two Fusou-class battleships, I am the younger sister, Yamashiro. Umm... have you seen Fusou nee-sama?
quotes.marriage: Th... ...Thank you. ...But... My heart shall always be with Fusou nee-sama's... I'm sorry.
quotes.married: The admiral, too... Please take a break sometime.

quotes.fleet_join: Tenryuu, torpedo squadron. Movin' out!
quotes.idle: What's up? A battle?
quotes.intro: My name is Tenryuu. Heheh. Ya scared?
quotes.marriage: Haha! Did ya fall in love with my power? Huh? Not my power, but me!? Ha! This is some kinda messed up dream, right!?
quotes.married: Hell yeah!

quotes.fleet_join: Time for a sortie. Now where's a ship who wants to die?
quotes.idle: Is there something on your mind?
quotes.intro: Nice to meet you, I'm Tatsuta~. I hope Tenryuu-chan hasn't been causing you trouble?
quotes.marriage: Having favour from the admiral is nice. B~ut, if I'm all friendly with the admiral, Tenryuu-chan will be all alone, you know~. I'm sorry, okay~?
quotes.married: Yay♪

quotes.fleet_join: Carrier Task Fleet, headin' out!
quotes.idle: What?
quotes.intro: Light aircraft carrier, Ryuujou! Ain't my silhouette distinctive? Actually... sendin' out planes one after another is right proper for a carrier, ya know! You can count on me!
quotes.marriage: By the way... Ahhh...! Don't worry, don't worry! You— what do you think of me? Sorry...! Well, pay me no mind. I'm just a li'l bit curious is all.
quotes.married: Let's give it a shot!

quotes.fleet_join: Mutsuki Fleet, ready for battle!
quotes.idle: Oyo? Admiral? You called for me?
quotes.intro: I'm Mutsuki. Let's show some enthusiasm!
quotes.marriage: To tell the truth, I wanted you to praise me, so I did my very, very best.
quotes.married: Oryo?

quotes.fleet_join: Kisaragi... starting the sortie!
quotes.idle: Did you call?
quotes.intro: My name is Kisaragi. Please keep me by your side.
quotes.marriage: Nn... it was all for show, to tell the truth. All I really wanted to do was gaze out at the sea with you... you know. Ah... just kidding♥
quotes.married: Just kidding♥

quotes.fleet_join: Satsuki, launch!
quotes.idle: Did ya call me?
quotes.intro: I'm Satsuki. Good to meet ya!
quotes.marriage: Commander! I'm sorry for always making you fret… but… it was a little on purpose… just kidding!
quotes.married: Leave it to me!

quotes.fleet_join: It's a sortie! I'll show you what I can do~!
quotes.idle: Eh? What, what?
quotes.intro: My name is Fumizuki. Nice to meet you~
quotes.marriage: Commander, why are you looking at me like that? Hweh~~! I'm a... a little nervous...!
quotes.married: Looking good!

quotes.fleet_join: Have you got the strategy hammered out? Then, off we go!
quotes.idle: What's up, Commander?
quotes.intro: Nagatsuki here. Don't make light of me as destroyers. I'm useful.
quotes.marriage: Relying on me so much is troubling... but it's not that simple. You're different, Commander.
quotes.married: This is nice.

quotes.fleet_join: Kikuzuki, moving out
quotes.idle: What is it?
quotes.intro: I'm Kikuzuki, let's move out together
quotes.marriage: If this war is over… can't I stay with you, Commander…? It can't be happening, can it…?
quotes.married: I won't say thanks...

quotes.fleet_join: Mikazuki, off to sortie!
quotes.idle: Good work today, Commander.
quotes.intro: You're the commander, right? I'm Mikazuki. I hope you welcome me warmly into your fleet.
quotes.marriage: I wanna get more and more strength to help everybody. But, the one I want to help the most is… Commander… Ah, pay it no mind… yeah…
quotes.married: With this, it looks like I'm good to go.
quotes.remodel: With this, it looks like I'm good to go.

quotes.fleet_join: A sortie~... Alright, everyone?
quotes.idle: What~? Commander.
quotes.intro: Hmm? Ah, I'm Mochizuki.
quotes.marriage: You really shouldn't be spending time and money on me… Now I just have to work harder…. But still, thank you.
quotes.married: nn… I'm not really that kind of character… but, well, Commander, maybe you should take a quick break, or something.

quotes.fleet_join: Kuma! Sortieing, kuma!
quotes.idle: Kuma?
quotes.intro: Kuma~ Nice to meet you, kuma.
quotes.marriage: Fufufu~ I've caught the admiral, kuma. I'm not gonna let you go, kuma. Kumakuma~!
quotes.married: Admiral, thanks for you hard work, kuma. Taking a break from time to time is good, kuma.

quotes.fleet_join: Tama, sortieing nya!
quotes.idle: Nyeh?
quotes.intro: Light cruiser, Tama. I'm not a cat, nya.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, please stop calling me with chan at the end, nya. It sort of... feels different, nya.
quotes.married: Thanks for the hard work, nya. Take a break with Tama, nya. Nyaa~

quotes.fleet_join: Where's the fool who dares challenge me?
quotes.idle: Someday, together with you... No, nothing. It's so unlike me too. Heh.
quotes.intro: It's Kiso. I'll bestow upon you absolute victory.
quotes.marriage: Don't mind me sayin' it, but your orders in battle send shivers through my spine. You're not half bad!
quotes.married: So it goes.

quotes.fleet_join: It's time! Leave it to me!
quotes.idle: Commander, thanks for the hard work!
quotes.intro: Light Cruiser Nagara! Please take good care of me!
quotes.marriage: Thank you for always leading us to victory! Nagara also loves the commander!
quotes.married: Yay!

quotes.fleet_join: Isuzu, sortieing! Continue!
quotes.idle: My preparation is always flawless!
quotes.intro: I'm Isuzu. Leave the torpedo squadrons to me. I'll bring victory to the admiral with all my power. Pleased to meet you.
quotes.marriage: The admirals I've had as my partners have all had great success. Isoroku, Tamon... I wonder what will become of you? I'm looking forward to it.
quotes.married: Idiot, don't worry so much. It's fine to take a break.

quotes.fleet_join: You called for me... Eh!? Sortie!?
quotes.idle: Um... W-what is it?
quotes.intro: I'm called Natori... I'll do my best not to trouble you!
quotes.marriage: The admiral doesn't really like fighting as well, it makes me feel at ease. For the admiral, no, for y-you… I'll keep doing my best.
quotes.married: Yeah! Then... that's all from me...
quotes.remodel: Yeah! Then... that's all from me...

quotes.fleet_join: Nagara-class Light Cruiser, Yura, heading out.
quotes.idle: What is it?
quotes.intro: Fourth ship of the Nagara-class Light Cruisers, 'Yura'. Pleased to make your acquaintance!
quotes.marriage: Did you, ummm, call me, Admiral? Eh, is it about my seaplanes? Ah, yes... I guess not? Ummm... is it about...? Eh?! About me...! No way... Eh... Really... No way... *snivel*
quotes.married: Admiral, it's definitely my single mounted guns, right? Right? Eh, what's that? You like my... hair too? Th-thanks... Umm... I, like you, too.

quotes.fleet_join: Sendai, torpedo squadron, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: What? A night battle?
quotes.intro: Sendai, reporting in! You can leave the night battles to me.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what's up? You're turning all red... ...Uh-huh♪ and then do you wanna have a night battle with me?
quotes.married: Admiral, you look worn out. You must be tired from the constant night battles. Yeah, I understand!

quotes.fleet_join: Jintsuu, heading out!
quotes.idle: Wha... what is it...?
quotes.intro: Um... I'm light cruiser Jintsuu... how... nice to meet you...
quotes.marriage: Every now and then, would it be okay to have a relaxing chat with you? ...Eh? Really? It's fine?
quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you tired? When you get a chance to rest, please do so, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Another job?
quotes.idle: Good morning~!
quotes.intro: The fleet's idol, Naka-chan! Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Thank you for all the support! I'm gonna work really, really hard for the admiral! Kira~n☆
quotes.married: Thank you~!

quotes.fleet_join: No problem, leave it to me.
quotes.idle: Admiral, what do you want to drink?
quotes.intro: I'm Chitose. I'm the the first Japanese seaplane tender. Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... After the battle's over, why don't we have a drink together? Ah, not some fuel!
quotes.married: Admiral, it's not good to work yourself too hard. Once in a while, won't you drink some fine sake with me, and have a little rest? Alright...?

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! Seaplane tender Chiyoda, launching!
quotes.idle: Eh? Did Chitose-onee do something again?
quotes.intro: Seaplane tender Chiyoda. My older sister Chitose isn't bothering you, is she?
quotes.marriage: Admiral, do you need something? Ah- You wanted to know if I'd seen Chitose-onee? I see...
quotes.married: Admiral, had you not seen Chitose-onee around here? Ah, is that so, hmm... well, then, umm... you look a little worn-out so I'll lend you my lap! I'll let you rest a little!

quotes.fleet_join: Mogami, setting off!
quotes.idle: Admiral! Oh, you're busy? I'm going out for some workout.
quotes.intro: I'm Mogami. It's alright, I won't collide with anyone this time. Really!
quotes.marriage: Ah, Admiral? Somehow, my rear cannon feels a bit off. Hey, could you take a quick look? Yeah, that's the spot…hey, that's not it!
quotes.married: I'm always crashing because I've only got eyes for you, Admiral! Just kidding!

quotes.fleet_join: Heavy cruiser Furutaka, heading out!
quotes.idle: This is a really great unit, you know?
quotes.intro: I'm Furutaka. I'll be happy to show how all the good points of heavy cruisers.
quotes.marriage: Admiral! How was the Heavy Cruiser team's performance? Did we make a difference? Awright, that's great! I'm so happy!
quotes.married: Awright!

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! It's my turn now!
quotes.idle: Fuaaa~. I'm sleepy.
quotes.intro: Second Furutaka Class Heavy Cruiser, name's Kako! Nice to meetcha!
quotes.marriage: Aaaahhhh, another scolding, yeah? Sorry for my carelessness, yeah? Wha- that's not it? Admiral… why is your face red?
quotes.married: Alright! Lucky!

quotes.fleet_join: Aoba covering... Ah, no, launching!
quotes.idle: Whatwhat? Got a story?
quotes.intro: Hi, thanks for your time, I'm Aoba! Please can I have some words!
quotes.marriage: Aoba, all she really wants to do is look at the commander rather than the enemy… J-just kidding!
quotes.married: Sorry to trouble you!

quotes.fleet_join: Myoukou, moving out.
quotes.idle: Admiral. Did you call for me?
quotes.intro: I am Myoukou, of the Myoukou-class Heavy Cruisers. Let us work on this together.
quotes.marriage: I greatly respect the admiral's fabulous strategy and tactics, and always shall.
quotes.married: If the admiral falls, I...please at least rest a bit when you are tired. It is Myoukou's wish.

quotes.fleet_join: Nachi's squadron! Heading out!!
quotes.idle: What do you want?
quotes.intro: You are my commander? I'm Nachi. I appreciate your contribution.
quotes.marriage: Hey you… Somehow… I don't hate you…. Yeah, as long as I am with you, I can promise more great victories. Definitely.
quotes.married: You, how are you doing? ...I see, it relieves me. We can sortie more together!

quotes.fleet_join: A sortie! The battleground is... Victory is calling out to me!
quotes.idle: What's the matter? Did something happen?
quotes.intro: Ashigara here. My specialty is surface combat. Fufu♪ Nice to meet you.
quotes.marriage: To have drawn out the full extent of my abilities... You are... ...I see. You're the first one to have done it!
quotes.married: Are you alright? Don't push yourself too hard, okay? Whether it's a rendezvous or a battle, the beginning is the most crucial part! Always face them in top condition!

quotes.fleet_join: Picking even me... I'll try my absolute best!
quotes.idle: Um... Commander?
quotes.intro: I'm Haguro. I'm the youngest of the Myoukou-class heavy cruiser sisters. U-um... I'm sorry!
quotes.marriage: After this battle is over… T-together with the commander..! Erm.. Ummm.. Errrmm…
quotes.married: Commander… I hope this war will be over and the sea will get quiet. I pray for it. Commander… you will surely…

quotes.fleet_join: Takao, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: Alriiight, the preparations for the sortie are finished... that aside... I wonder if Atago is working properly... Oh? Admiral? Fufu♪ ...It's fine.
quotes.intro: Hello. I'm Takao. I'm glad that you seem like an excellent Admiral.
quotes.marriage: These words of praise... perhaps you could express them in a clearer way... Not a medal, but...
quotes.married: Admiral, I'm right here with you... so rest easy.

quotes.fleet_join: Atago, setting sail~!
quotes.idle: Admiral? Well, now... it looks like Takao might be running a little low on calcium. I wonder if she should drink more milk. A-ouch! Hey... Takao!
quotes.intro: I'm Atago. Admiral, please remember that, okay?
quotes.marriage: As a reward... for a little while, you and I can swap hats... and see how we look. *swap* Ufufufu♪
quotes.married: Ufufufufu! I'm all flustered♪

quotes.fleet_join: Yeah! Let's go! Setting sail!
quotes.idle: Huh...?
quotes.intro: Yo! Name's Maya, nice to meet you.
quotes.marriage: Thanks for always using my full power, man. This too... I thank...you.
quotes.married: You...can be kind sometimes...I guess.

quotes.fleet_join: Setting sail! Choukai, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: Ah... Commander! Thanks for the hard work.
quotes.intro: My name is Choukai. It's a pleasure.
quotes.marriage: If you're ever perplexed by a strategy, you can always come to me. We'll analyze it— just the two of us!
quotes.married: I'm... forever grateful to you. It's an honor to be with you.

quotes.fleet_join: Come now! To the front!
quotes.idle: Good. I shall go!
quotes.intro: I am Tone! With my addition to the fleet, there will be no problems searching out the enemy!
quotes.marriage: That's right, my scouts have found the enemy fleet!! ...Eh? Enough of that? ...Then what is it? What is this?
quotes.married: I did it!

quotes.fleet_join: Chikuma, all preparations complete! Heading out!
quotes.idle: Tone nee-san? Oh, it's just you Admiral.
quotes.intro: Pleased to meet you. Second of the Tone-class, Chikuma.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, calling me out to this place... I... my heart is set on my oneesan... Eh? It's about formations? Oh my... Even me...
quotes.married: I did it!

quotes.fleet_join: Now then, Hiyou-class aircraft carrier's setting off!
quotes.idle: What? I'm busy...
quotes.intro: My name is Izumo Ma... No, Hiyou. I'm an aircraft carrier. Pleased to meet you, Admiral!
quotes.marriage: A-ah... Why…? Somehow fleet work is tiring… Ah, sorry to be grumbling to Admiral… I-it's okay?...
quotes.married: You don't look too good, Admiral. Don't work yourself too hard. You'll feel better after getting some rest, really!

quotes.fleet_join: Let's do this! Junyou, headin' out!
quotes.idle: A~dmiral. If you got a sec then gimme a ha~nd. Hiyou an' me, we need some good planes, y'know?
quotes.intro: Merchant ship turned carrier, Junyou here~! Hyaha!
quotes.marriage: I worked really hard so I wouldn't lose to those standard carriers. You're the only admiral who really gets me, y'know what I mean? Hey... Gimme a kiss♥
quotes.married: Yo~ Admiral, you wanna have a drink with me sometime? I got some really good sake♪ Ah, don't worry. I brought some snacks, too.

quotes.fleet_join: Ayanami-class Destroyer, Oboro, heading out!
quotes.idle: I'll do my best!
quotes.intro: I'm the Ayanami-class destroyer Oboro. I won't lose to anyone. Probably.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, am I of use to you? Well then, that's great...
quotes.married: I won't lose!

quotes.fleet_join: Akebono, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: What? What is it?
quotes.intro: Special Type destroyer, Akebono here. Hey! Don't look at me, you shitty admiral!
quotes.marriage: You must think you're Mr. Perfect for calling me out to such a place, Shitty Admiral... Anyway, what's up with you confessing to me? Are you a masochist!?
quotes.married: This really isn't funny.

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Sazanami, going!
quotes.idle: Master?
quotes.intro: Ayanami-class destroyer Sazanami here, Master. You write it like this, but read it as "Sazanami".
quotes.marriage: Welcome back, Master~! ...Er... huh? Admiral, you got your serious face on... Huh? Huh, huh? Eeeh?
quotes.married: There it is!

quotes.fleet_join: Ushio, moving out.
quotes.idle: Maybe... did you call for me?
quotes.intro: I'm the Special Type Ayanami-class destroyer, Ushio. It would be nice if I could be dismissed soon...
quotes.marriage: Admiral, that is... I'll adore... no, umm... respect you! Yes! Always!
quotes.married: I'll save everyone I possibly can!
quotes.remodel: I'll save everyone I possibly can!

quotes.fleet_join: It is my turn now, yes? Please observe.
quotes.idle: Commander, good day to you.
quotes.intro: I'm Akatsuki! Treat me like the fully-fledged lady I am!
quotes.marriage: To dine alone with the commander, as a lady... Huh? Why do I only have juice? Furthermore, why does the pilaf have a flag on it...!
quotes.married: C-Co-Co-Commander! For working so hard, I shall offer you my praise. Please lower your head.

quotes.fleet_join: Roger. Hibiki, heading out.
quotes.idle: Commander, what is it?
quotes.intro: I'm Hibiki. I'm also known as the "Phoenix" from my exploits.
quotes.marriage: Commander, things like love and passion... what are they...? Huh? You'll teach me?
quotes.married: Commander, aren't you tired?

quotes.fleet_join: Yes, Commander! Here I go!
quotes.idle: You look worn out. That won't do at all!
quotes.intro: I'm Ikazuchi! Don't read my name as "Kaminari"! You'll do well to remember that!
quotes.marriage: Hey, Commander. If I wasn't here, the fleet would fall apart. Right? Right?
quotes.married: Commander, you'll be just fine. After all, I'm right here beside you!

quotes.fleet_join: Watch what I can do when I'm serious!
quotes.idle: Hawawawa! You surprised me!
quotes.intro: I'm Inazuma. How... nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Commander, you're still here, I see. Huh? You were waiting for me? ...Thank you.
quotes.married: Commander, you've looked so tired lately, nanodesu. I'll give you a shoulder massage.

quotes.fleet_join: Hatsuharu, casting off!
quotes.idle: Oh, are you interested in us?
quotes.intro: We are Hatsuharu. We thank you in advance.
quotes.marriage: You...!? W-w-w-w-aaa! To expose us to such shameful words! Shame on you! For shame...
quotes.married: We are, somehow... joyful.

quotes.fleet_join: I have been waiting for it!
quotes.idle: What day is today? It's Nenohi day!
quotes.intro: Hello, it's Nenohi. I hope my name wasn't hard to read, yes?
quotes.marriage: Hey, do you know day is today? ...Gee, it's Nenohi! No, that's no it, it's the day Nenohi will confess. To who, you asked? Admiral, you meanie!
quotes.married: I wonder what kind of day today will be~
quotes.remodel: I wonder what day is today?

quotes.fleet_join: Wakaba, launching.
quotes.idle: I'm Wakaba.
quotes.intro: Destroyer, Wakaba.
quotes.marriage: The miracle battle, Kiska! Kiss… ka? Hey, wait! Your face is too close!
quotes.married: Even without sleep for 24 hours I'm okay.
quotes.remodel: Even without sleep for 24 hours I'm okay.

quotes.fleet_join: Hatsushimo, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Preparations, complete.
quotes.intro: Fourth ship of the Hatsuharu class, Hatsushimo. Everyone, I'm very pleased to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Kiska... Ah, I'm sorry! I'm not interested in romance right now... even so, will you wait for me...?
quotes.married: That did it!

quotes.fleet_join: Ok~ay, let's go all out!
quotes.idle: Whatwhat? My turn?
quotes.intro: First ship of the Shiratsuyu-class destroyers, 'Shiratsuyu'!. Yes, the first ship!
quotes.marriage: *laugh* Admiral, what a nice feeling. My number one favourite thing? It's a se~cret!
quotes.married: I want the admiral to become everybody's number one~ Yeah! Today's a number one smile!

quotes.fleet_join: Shigure, moving out!
quotes.idle: Am I still supposed to be here...?
quotes.intro: I'm Shigure, of the Shiratsuyu-class destroyers. Nice to meet you.
quotes.marriage: The rain... looks like it isn't stopping. Admiral, you'll get soaked over there, you know? Why don't you come a little closer? Until the rain lifts, let's stay like this.
quotes.married: A hard-working admiral is great as well. Still, don't push yourself too hard, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Murasame going o~ut!
quotes.idle: Yesye~s!
quotes.intro: Yes ye~s! I'm the Shiratsuyu-class destroyer 'Murasame'! Everyone, nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Just the two of us, it's suprisingly fun, I think. Hey, the compatbility between us is good, yeah?
quotes.married: Admiral, when you're feeling down, Murasame will give you some of her spirit! There! Well? Feeling better?

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Yuudachi, gonna sortie!
quotes.idle: Umm... are you leaving me, poi? Am I still not good enough, poi!? Then I'll have to train more and more!
quotes.intro: Hello. I'm the Shiratsuyu-class destroyer, Yuudachi. I'm in your care!
quotes.marriage: Admiral-san, your face is so red, poi. Why? You want to talk about love? The person I like? Eh... no way, what should I...?
quotes.married: If it's for Admiral-san's sake, I can get so much stronger, poi!

quotes.fleet_join: At last it's finally our turn.
quotes.idle: Admiral, I'll do my very best!
quotes.intro: My name is Samidare! I look forward to working with you. Please leave any escort missions to me!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, I...the admiral...I li...NOTHING! I'll do my best from now on too!
quotes.married: Please leave it to me.

quotes.fleet_join: I understand! I'll show the serious Suzukaze!
quotes.idle: Is it my turn?
quotes.intro: 'ello! I'm Suzukaze. If I join the fleet it will be equivalent to 100 ships!
quotes.marriage: Emmm. I… the A...admira… li... Ugh. ...Nothing....You're wrong! I said nothing!
quotes.married: It's perfect!

quotes.fleet_join: Asashio, heading out!
quotes.idle: Commander, your orders.
quotes.intro: Destroyer Asashio here. I'm always prepared in case of a battle.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? To call me out to such a place... just the two of us... Ah, this is... a strategy meeting, isn't it!
quotes.married: U-um... this may be presumptuous coming from me, however... I've always had the utmost respect for you!

quotes.fleet_join: Here I go~!!!
quotes.idle: I'm always going full speed ahead!
quotes.intro: Destroyer Ooshio here~! A small body with large torpedoes! Please leave it to me!
quotes.marriage: Are you familiar with the meaning behind "Ooshio"? It's when the gravitational pull of the moon brings the waves closer. You could say it's just like the two of us.
quotes.married: Commander, how've you been? Are your days fulfilling?

quotes.fleet_join: Michishio, heading out!
quotes.idle: ...That's annoying.
quotes.intro: Michishio here. Why was I assigned to a unit like this?
quotes.marriage: Haven't the battles been going better compared to how it was at first? I don't dislike that.
quotes.married: Ho-nestly, this unit is so half-assed. We're not here to act like close friends, you know! ...You're saying I'm one of you...? I-It's not like I'm happy about that...

quotes.fleet_join: Arashio, sortieing gorgeously.
quotes.idle: Ufufufufu... still resupplying?
quotes.intro: My, I haven't introduced myself yet, have I? I'm Arashio!
quotes.marriage: Ufufufu... I'm rather persistent, but... I wonder if you can endure it...
quotes.married: As for you, everyone admires you, you know? Even that Michishio-chan... doesn't she really? Ufufufufu...

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Arare, casting off.
quotes.idle: Commander..... is there something, to do?
quotes.intro: Arare... I won't say 'ncha-'... Look after me...
quotes.marriage: Ah… Commander, what is it? I want to get back to work.. Yeah…
quotes.married: 'ncha...

quotes.fleet_join: Kasumi, departing! I can't just stand by and watch.
quotes.idle: Look me in the eyes if you need me for something.
quotes.intro: It's Kasumi. I'm charging in. Follow me.
quotes.marriage: Oh, finding a trashy commander like you in a place like this must mean you have a lot of time on your hands, huh~? ... ...Eh... a present? For me? Eh... ah... ... ...idiot...!
quotes.married: W-What!? I'm actually a little grateful to you. It'd get lonely without you. ...D-Don't get the wrong idea!

quotes.fleet_join: At last, it's my turn!
quotes.idle: Time to go?
quotes.intro: We've finally met! I'm Kagerou. Treat me well!
quotes.marriage: Ah, Commander! Great work!... Erm, right.. Um, here's a Hawaiian souvenir chocolate for you!
quotes.married: Yay!

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo squadron, sortie!
quotes.idle: Did you call for me, Commander?
quotes.intro: I'm Shiranui. I look forward to your guidance and encouragement.
quotes.marriage: Commander, what do you think of my battles...? Oh, I see... Well, that's fine too.
quotes.married: So-so.

quotes.fleet_join: Well then, Kuroshio, off I go!
quotes.idle: Yep, I'm goin'!
quotes.intro: I'm Kuroshio, nice to meet 'cha!
quotes.marriage: I... I'm... always lookin' at the chief, y'know? Really! C'mon, believe me...
quotes.married: Bit-by-bit~

quotes.fleet_join: Fleet, time to sortie!
quotes.idle: One dive bomber... two dive bombers... three... Ah, Admiral! It's okay, I'm not lonely or anything. I have my planes with me and... Ah, yes!
quotes.intro: I'm the light aircraft carrier, Shouhou. Yes, I'm a little small, but please make a place for me on your fleet!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... From now on, I'll always be by your side! ...Am I being useful? Really? Then...that's great.
quotes.married: Once in a while, won't you try taking it easy and be yourself? Forget about things like sortie and your duty... I mean, I'm sorry! That's no good, isn't it...

quotes.fleet_join: No problem, leave it to me.
quotes.idle: You're busy aren't you? That's fine, that's fine. How about we take it easy?
quotes.intro: I'm Chitose. I'm the the first Japanese seaplane tender. Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... After the battle's over, why don't we have a drink together? Ah, not some fuel!
quotes.married: Admiral, it's not good to work yourself too hard. Once in a while, won't you drink some fine sake with me, and have a little rest? Alright...?

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! Seaplane tender Chiyoda, launching!
quotes.idle: Admiral, it's Chiyoda! Did you forget about me?
quotes.intro: Seaplane tender Chiyoda. My older sister Chitose isn't bothering you, is she?
quotes.marriage: Admiral, do you need something? Ah- You wanted to know if I'd seen Chitose-onee? I see...
quotes.married: Admiral, had you not seen Chitose-onee around here? Ah, is that so, hmm... well, then, umm... you look a little worn-out so I'll lend you my lap! I'll let you rest a little!

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo Cruiser Ooi, heading out!
quotes.idle: Will Kitakami-san be alright?..... I'm getting worried as I'm not with her... Hmm... I'm so worried... It's definitely, yes, there's definitely something that's about to happen! I have to go now!
quotes.intro: I'm torpedo cruiser Ooi. By the way, I wonder where Kitakami-san is.
quotes.marriage: Of the two Torpedo cruisers, you chose me, right?... If you betray me, I'll sink you in the ocean, you know...
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened to the other girls, you say? Eh...? That's not it? Hmm, it's okay then.. It's okay...
quotes.remodel: If Kitakami is fine with it, go ahead.

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo cruiser Kitakami, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: For some reason... My shoulder is all stiff, y'know— my shoulder. But I'm still so young, y'know~ I guess torpedoes are really kinda heavy, y'know~?
quotes.intro: A brand new Kitakami... that's who I am. I feel a little more mature, loaded to the brim with oxygen torpedoes like this♪
quotes.marriage: Admiral, I have a favor to ask, yeah. That one weapon... I don't really want to use it. ...Countin' on ya.
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened? Ya feelin' down? That's not like ya. Everything's fine!

quotes.fleet_join: No problem, leave it to me.
quotes.idle: You're busy aren't you? That's fine, that's fine. How about we take it easy?
quotes.intro: I'm Chitose. I'm the the first Japanese seaplane tender. Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... After the battle's over, why don't we have a drink together? Ah, not some fuel!
quotes.married: Admiral, it's not good to work yourself too hard. Once in a while, won't you drink some fine sake with me, and have a little rest? Alright...?

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! Seaplane tender Chiyoda, launching!
quotes.idle: Admiral, it's Chiyoda! Did you forget about me?
quotes.intro: Seaplane tender Chiyoda. My older sister Chitose isn't bothering you, is she?
quotes.marriage: Admiral, do you need something? Ah- You wanted to know if I'd seen Chitose-onee? I see...
quotes.married: Admiral, had you not seen Chitose-onee around here? Ah, is that so, hmm... well, then, umm... you look a little worn-out so I'll lend you my lap! I'll let you rest a little!

quotes.fleet_join: Aviation cruiser Mogami, launching!
quotes.idle: Admiral! Oh, you're busy? I'm going out for some workout.
quotes.intro: We meet again, Admiral. It's Mogami. How's my flight deck? Does it suit me?
quotes.marriage: Admiral, wassup? What's with that look? Is there something up with my flight deck?
quotes.married: I'm always crashing because I've only got eyes for you, Admiral! Just kidding!

quotes.fleet_join: Aviation battleship 'Ise' launching!
quotes.idle: Ah, sorry. Did you call me?
quotes.intro: I'm the aviation battleship 'Ise'! With a rear-facing flight deck and 2 catapults, I can make use of the power of aviation!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, erm... Could you please not take my catapult away... If I don't have that, I'll... Ah! You meanie!
quotes.married: Isn't this nice?

quotes.fleet_join: Fourth Carrier Division, moving out!
quotes.idle: Oh... It's you. You're still here.
quotes.intro: Ise-class Aviation Battleship, Hyuuga... Pushing forward.
quotes.marriage: Aviation Battleship... Got a nice ring to it, yeah? You get it, right? Alright... let's drink! We're not going back 'till morning!
quotes.married: Yeah... I expected that.

quotes.fleet_join: Fellow planes, off we go!
quotes.idle: You're busy aren't you? That's fine, that's fine. How about we take it easy?
quotes.intro: I'm the girl who took a diet and became an aircraft carrier, Chitose. I even got faster. Maybe I should write a book about it.
quotes.marriage: Thank you for always looking out for the reborn Chitose, Admiral.
quotes.married: The admiral is always doing his utmost best. It's okay. I understand.

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft carrier Chiyoda, launching!
quotes.idle: Admiral, it's Chiyoda! Did you forget about me?
quotes.intro: The girl that became an aircraft carrier, Chiyoda. Of course, I'll be assigned to Chitose-onee's fleet, yes?
quotes.marriage: Admiral.... I'm happy that you have feelings for me... But still, I'm worried about Chitose-onee...
quotes.married: Even though I'm worried for just Chitose-onee, the admiral upon that... really, good grief.

quotes.fleet_join: CarDiv 5, Shoukaku, starting the sortie!
quotes.idle: Admiral? Um... we should be heading to Port Moresby... Um... that is...
quotes.intro: First of the Shoukaku-class carriers, Shoukaku here. I will try to live up to the names of my senpai in CarDiv 1 and CarDiv 2, fighting hard alongside Zuikaku!
quotes.marriage: Admiral? Maybe... Thank you so much. Just maybe... if my wish comes true... After Marianas... You and I can always... You've loaded these wonderful planes that I had never seen before. I'm truly overflowing with this feeling of gratitude!
quotes.married: Admiral, I'm always really grateful for your hard work. Please take a short break, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: CarDiv 5, Zuikaku, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Admiral...! You know, I'm getting really bored here... I'm gonna throw a fit...
quotes.intro: Second of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, the younger sister, Zuikaku. The lucky carrier, you say? That's not it— I just fight with all my might... see? As long as I still have planes, I won't lose!
quotes.marriage: Admiral-san... You're too close! Your face... Ah.. ah~h~h...! ...What's up...? Ah... That's such a serious look... Is there something on my face? Eh? Ah! Too close!
quotes.married: Admiral-san... you shouldn't overdo it, you know...?

quotes.fleet_join: CarDiv 5, Zuikaku, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Admiral...! You know, I'm getting really bored here... I'm gonna throw a fit...
quotes.intro: Second of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, the younger sister, Zuikaku. The lucky carrier, you say? That's not it— I just fight with all my might... see? As long as I still have planes, I won't lose!
quotes.marriage: Admiral-san... You're too close! Your face... Ah.. ah~h~h...! ...What's up...? Ah... That's such a serious look... Is there something on my face? Eh? Ah! Too close!
quotes.married: Admiral-san... you shouldn't overdo it, you know...?

quotes.fleet_join: Light cruiser Kinu, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: Admiral...! Can't we go train or something soon~?
quotes.intro: I'm here, I'm here! Kinu has arrived at long last!
quotes.marriage: Admiral! We're always just training together, so maybe it's a sign that we should spend more time... together... Eh!? No, I didn't mean it that way. I mean the one closest to you should protect you... I just want to... ohhh... ... ...whatever!
quotes.married: Admiral! You want a shoulder massage? Or maybe you wanna go train?

quotes.fleet_join: Huh, no way, me!? I-I can go but...
quotes.idle: Geez! I thought you might have forgotten about me!
quotes.intro: H-hello, I'm Abukuma, a light cruiser.
quotes.marriage: Admiral~, thanks for waiting! I want to say couple of words of thanks to you… because you looked after me with such care, I got a bit more confident. Admiral, thank you.
quotes.married: Admiral, please don't overdo it, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Heading out! W-wait, I'm the slowest here, don't leave me behind!
quotes.idle: Mr. Hiraga's talent is so beautiful.. Huh? Oh Admiral, you were here!?
quotes.intro: Oka~y, thanks for waiting! The experimental armament cruiser 'Yuubari' has arrived!
quotes.marriage: I know some people think I'm a bit of an armament geek, but… that's not exactly it. I wanted to collect the best data for you, Admiral… really! That's really the truth…
quotes.married: ♪ Leave it to me, okay? Commander.
quotes.remodel: The data was right on the mark!

quotes.fleet_join: Light aircraft carrier, Zuihou. Now heading out!
quotes.idle: Coastal patrol and transport fleet escort are both important things aren't they....Hey, Admiral, let's go do some work..
quotes.intro: I'm Zuihou. I'm a light carrier, but with proper experience, I'll be able to show you that I perform as good as an aircraft carrier.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? Eh? A bouquet...? Eh? For me!? Ah, ah, what should I do… Th-Th-Thank… you. Is it an air group inspection… it's not? Ah, your face is all serious…
quotes.married: Admiral, thanks for all the hard work. Looking after all us light aircraft carriers so well… it makes me happy.

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft Carrier, Zuihou! Setting sail now!
quotes.idle: Coastal patrol and transport fleet escort are both important things aren't they....Hey, Admiral, let's go do some work..
quotes.intro: I'm Zuihou. How do my remodeled clothes look? I'll still do my best!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? Eh? A bouquet...? Eh? For me!? Ah, ah, what should I do… Th-Th-Thank… you. Is it an air group inspection… it's not? Ah, your face is all serious…
quotes.married: Admiral? Umm... I, think made too much tamagoyaki... will you eat it? Aah, really? Ehehe... I'm glad.
quotes.remodel: My bento, will you eat it?

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo Cruiser Ooi, heading out!
quotes.idle: Will Kitakami-san be alright?..... I'm getting worried as I'm not with her... Hmm... I'm so worried... It's definitely, yes, there's definitely something that's about to happen! I have to go now!
quotes.intro: I'm torpedo cruiser Ooi. By the way, I wonder where Kitakami-san is.
quotes.marriage: Of the two Torpedo cruisers, you chose me, right?... If you betray me, I'll sink you in the ocean, you know...
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened to the other girls, you say? Eh...? That's not it? Hmm, it's okay then.. It's okay...

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo cruiser Kitakami, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: For some reason... My shoulder is all stiff, y'know— my shoulder. But I'm still so young, y'know~ I guess torpedoes are really kinda heavy, y'know~?
quotes.intro: A brand new Kitakami... that's who I am. I feel a little more mature, loaded to the brim with oxygen torpedoes like this♪
quotes.marriage: Well... what to say? Oh, yeah... doesn't this feel nice? Lately... I kinda think like that, but... yeah... Well, that's kinda how it is?
quotes.married: Admiral? What happened? Ya feelin' down? That's not like ya. Everything's fine!

quotes.fleet_join: Yes! Admiral, let's go together!
quotes.idle: Really, Admiral... I thought you'd forgotten about me.
quotes.intro: Greetings, I'm Mikuma. I wonder where Mogami could be hiding?
quotes.marriage: Admiral, for taking such great care of me up until now, my gratitude is boundless. Umm.. If it's okay, afterwards, together with Mikuma…. Kumarinko!
quotes.married: I'll certainly repay this kindness.
quotes.remodel: Would it be alright if I said 'Kumakuma'?

quotes.fleet_join: Aviation cruiser Mikuma, setting off!
quotes.idle: Really, Admiral... I thought you'd forgotten about me.
quotes.intro: Admiral, I've attained a new form!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, for taking such great care of me up until now, my gratitude is boundless. Umm.. If it's okay, afterwards, together with Mikuma…. Kumarinko!
quotes.married: I'll certainly repay this kindness.
quotes.remodel: Would it be alright if I said 'Kumakuma'?

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Hatsukaze, setting off!
quotes.idle: Ah, geez, I'm so bored~! Admiral, do something~
quotes.intro: I'm Hatsukaze, nice to meet you. Admiral, how many of me did you have before me, I wonder?
quotes.marriage: Why're you calling me over here? I'm busy with maintenance and replenishment… eh? What? Such a large bouquet… for me? No way... I'm so happy… I'm...wha..what are you making me say, you stupid Admiral!? I-I'll just keep it!
quotes.married: Admiral, just where are you looking? Hatsukaze's right here.

quotes.fleet_join: Nice decision! Admiral~
quotes.idle: Hey, won't you dance, Admiral?
quotes.intro: Hello~! Kagerou-class destroyer, Maikaze! I'm not good in gloomy atmospheres!
quotes.marriage: This is something I can only say to you, Admiral... truthfully, I can't help being scared... so I distract myself by dancing... But, with the admiral by my side, everything is alright... can I stay close to you some more...?
quotes.married: Admiral~ come and dance with me~!

quotes.fleet_join: Leave it to Miss Kinugasa!
quotes.idle: Oi! Ooi! Oh, you're not Ooi? Ah, he glared at me.
quotes.intro: Ye~s, It's Miss Kinugasa's debut! Together with Aoba, take good care of me!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, so that I can protect you, I'm gonna get stronger and stronger! But, if it get dangerous, you have to promise to get away, okay? I don't want to lose someone important to me.
quotes.married: You okay? You're not ti~red?

quotes.fleet_join: Fellow planes, off we go!

quotes.marriage: Thank you for always looking out for the reborn Chitose, Admiral.
quotes.married: The admiral is always doing his utmost best. It's okay. I understand.

quotes.married: Admiral! Did you see Chitose-onee? Is that so? Then, erm...! Yo... you seem a little tired so I'll lend you my lap to rest on!

quotes.married: A~dmi~ra~l! I'll massage your shoulders! ...Uuu, they're all stiff...

quotes.idle: Admiraaal, I am seriously bored here... aren't we gonna sortie? I-want-to-sor-tie!

quotes.marriage: Admiral! I know I'm getting kinda serious on you, but thanks for trusting a ship like me with so many jobs! Just wanted to say thanks... ehe♪ ...Eh... ah... well anyway, as always, I'm in your care!
quotes.married: That girl, Kumano... I hope she's doing okay... right, Admiral?

quotes.fleet_join: Understood.
quotes.idle: N… n ~u~u…… fu ~a~a… Im feeling a bit sleepy
quotes.intro: Good day to you. I am the heavy cruiser Kumano.
quotes.marriage: The admiral's room, it has such a pleasant feel to it, yes? I do not dislike it. At any rate, if you make such a request, it will be fine to stay, no? Yes, if it is your desire…
quotes.married: Admiral. W-well... You appear to be doing quite well? I just might praise you, you know.

quotes.fleet_join: It's time to deploy, I'll show you the power of a Kaidai-class submarine!
quotes.idle: Commander, did you come to hate Imuya?
quotes.intro: I'm I-168. What? It's hard to say? OK, just call me Imuya. Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Commander, I can dive to about 100m. Won't you come dive with me this time? I, will guide you with all my strength. When this fight is over... it's a promise, okay?
quotes.married: Commander, let's take a break if you are tired.

quotes.fleet_join: Goya, diving!
quotes.idle: Aaadmiral, Goya is lonelyyy...

quotes.marriage: Being with the admiral is so much fun! You know, there are lots of fish that only live in the south, they're worth seeing, yeah? This time, I'll take you there!
quotes.married: Do your best with your KanColle study!

quotes.fleet_join: Hacchan, heading out.

quotes.married: Admiral, overworking is bad, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Mogami-class aviation cruiser, Suzuya! Here I go~!
quotes.idle: Admiraaal, I am seriously bored here... aren't we gonna sortie? I-want-to-sor-tie!
quotes.intro: I'm Suzuya! What a lively fleet this is. I'm in your care!

quotes.married: That girl, Kumano... I hope she's doing okay... right, Admiral?

quotes.fleet_join: Understood.
quotes.idle: N… n ~u~u…… fu ~a~a… Im feeling a bit sleepy
quotes.intro: Good day to you. I am the heavy cruiser Kumano.
quotes.marriage: The admiral's room, it has such a pleasant feel to it, yes? I do not dislike it. At any rate, if you make such a request, it will be fine to stay, no? Yes, if it is your desire…
quotes.married: Admiral. W-well... You appear to be doing quite well? I just might praise you, you know.

quotes.marriage: Admiral, as always, thank you so much. That I love the most. I will... Always, Admiral... At my darling's side, I shall do my best. Even more than serving as flagship of the Combined Fleet... More than fighting enemy battleships... It's now... This moment...
quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you feeling a bit tired?

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Akigumo! Heading o~ut!
quotes.idle: Waaaa! That's it! It's almost the submission deadline, isn't it! I can't just sit around!

quotes.marriage: At last the admiral has been caught by my charm~? Ju~st kidding! But I wonder what kind of picture the future of me and the admiral would be… Should I seriously try drawing a thin book? Wouldn't it be great?
quotes.married: Admiral, are you beat? Well then, Akigumo will draw a picture of you♪

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Yuugumo, going with full force!
quotes.idle: Aren't you tired Admiral? Yuugumo is quite worried you know...

quotes.marriage: Ah, Admiral~, your hat is askance again. You're the commander of such a big fleet, please do look the part. Just how much do I have to look after you… eh? It's fine to keep on doing it? Well, that's・just・lovely♡
quotes.married: Admiral~ is it not a good time to take a quick break?

quotes.fleet_join: It's Makigumo's turn, I'll do my best!
quotes.idle: ...I'm always looking at Commander-sama from the screen.
quotes.intro: Yuugumo-class destroyer, I am Makigumo. Following Yuugumo-neesan's example, I'll do my best!
quotes.marriage: Commander-sama, thank you very much for letting me take my time today. Makigumo too, has to graduate from Yuugumo-neesan some time. Is that okay?
quotes.married: Commander-sama, do your be~st! Makigumo will too!

quotes.fleet_join: Now, let's go do a replay of Savo!
quotes.idle: Hmm, if you're not going to sortie, how about a nap? The night's long.
quotes.intro: I'm Naganami, the fourth ship of the Yuugumo-class destroyers. And off we go. Yeah!
quotes.marriage: What is it? With that glum face and all.If you keep acting that way, it'll spread to the entire fleet, you know. Well, I'll lend this Naganami's chest to you here. Now, spit out your problems. Now, in a big voice! Eh? I-it's that!? Well, that's fine too, I guess...
quotes.married: Aa~, of course I get you, Admiral. How lovely~

quotes.fleet_join: Flagship Yamato, now sortieing!
quotes.idle: Mm... ah... Admiral, I apologize. Is my main battery getting in the way?
quotes.intro: First of the Yamato-class battleships, Yamato, now with drastically improved anti-air weaponry.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, as always, thank you so much. That I love the most. I will... Always, Admiral... At my darling's side, I shall do my best. Even more than serving as flagship of the Combined Fleet... More than fighting enemy battleships... It's now... This moment...

quotes.idle: Agano-class, first ship, Agano, will be waiting for you all the time, right? Admiral?

quotes.married: Admira~l! Yes! Do your best!

quotes.married: Admiral, just one more push. Come on!
quotes.remodel: Is Agano-nee going to be okay with this?

quotes.fleet_join: Leave the Second Torpedo Squardon to me. This is Yahagi, raising anchor!
quotes.idle: Right... If there can be another life for me after this one, I guess becoming something other than a warship wouldn't be such a bad idea.
quotes.intro: Light Cruiser Yahagi, reporting for duty. Let's work at it together to the end, Admiral!
quotes.marriage: Wha-, Admiral, you.. What's wrong? Your face... you have a rather serious expression. ...Eh, this is for me? Not for someone like Yamato or Yukikaze? For me!? W-what should I do... hu-hum.... What should I do..I-I...
quotes.married: Admiral… The fleet girls are complimenting you for your hard work, you know? ...he isn't listening...

quotes.fleet_join: Light Cruiser Sakawa, setting sail! Watch me closely!

quotes.married: You okay? You're not ti~red?

quotes.marriage: Don't mind me sayin' it, but your orders in battle send shivers through my spine. You're not half bad!

quotes.married: Commander, aren't you tired?

quotes.fleet_join: Off I go! With all my spirit! Held high!

quotes.marriage: If my predictions hold true, after the battle is over, ...No, it was nothing! I believe you and I are going to... most likely... most likely...♪

quotes.remodel: Hm... this is a good thing.

quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you tired? Really? Well, that's okay. But don't overdo it… okay?

quotes.marriage: Admiral.. Did I meet your expectations? But I've still got much more to go. Let's stay together and do our best! Well, that's great♪
quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you tired? Really? Well, that's okay. But don't overdo it… okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Sendai, DesRon3, sortieing!

quotes.marriage: Every now and then, would it be okay to have a relaxing chat with you? ...Eh? Really? It's fine?
quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you tired? When you get a chance to rest, please do so, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Another job?

quotes.intro: I'm the fleet's idol, Naka-chan! I'm always cute~!
quotes.marriage: Thank you for all the support! I'm gonna work really, really hard for the admiral! Kira~n☆
quotes.married: Thank you~!

quotes.married: Admiral, I brought you some tea. Okay, roger that. I'll get it for you right away. Ufufu♪ It's Japanese Shincha. Is that okay? I can also get you some fine fragrant black tea.

quotes.married: Commande~r, if you're tired let's take a break together! Pyon pyon!

quotes.fleet_join: Akitsu Maru, Daihatsu and Ka-types are ready to go.

quotes.marriage: I thought that you had no concerns about me. Oh, beg your pardon. I would like to know more and more about you, sir. The strength of this feeling is connected... As expected of Admiral...
quotes.married: Admiral, there are no ship daughters that you will never get a chance to meet. I can say this, for it is in this way that I, too, have managed to meet you…

quotes.idle: Mmmmm, I'd like to go out soon.

quotes.idle: Eeeeeek! I'm bored anyway. Why not go somewhere to have a night battle?
quotes.intro: Admiral, I'm Tanikaze! I'll be in your care from now on.
quotes.marriage: What a strange admiral you are to be interested in me, Tanikaze! Then, tell me how you get to love me from the beginning. Hehe, it's fine, the night is long, you know.
quotes.married: Admiral, what's up? Are you tired?

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Hamakaze, moving out!
quotes.idle: The breeze is pleasant again today, isn't it?
quotes.intro: I'm destroyer Hamakaze. Henceforth I shall be assigned to your fleet.
quotes.marriage: Admiral. If it's about matchmaking, don't you think there are plenty of other girls you can ask who are more into that? ...Eh? Me? N-No! I... this sort of thing... b-but, I'll face it head-on, study it, and put all of my effort into it... okay...?
quotes.married: Admiral, aren't you getting tired?

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Bismarck, setting sail! Sally forth!
quotes.idle: Geez~! To neglect one such as myself, aren't you quite something! It's fine for me to come along on a sortie or practice, you know!?
quotes.intro: Guten tag. I am Bismarck, the nameship of the Bismarck-class battleships. You should remember it well.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? I won't give this back, you know? Definitely... Such an earnest expression... This is for me? ...I-I see... Y-you can give it to me.
quotes.married: Admiral, no matter what it is, it's bad to work too hard, okay? A change of pace is also a good thing, you know?

quotes.idle: Ah, It's not that I'm bored, I'm just fine, yep.
quotes.intro: Guten morgen. I'm Leberecht Maass. Lebe is fine. ...Yeah.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, why the serious face? Eh? What's this box... O-oh. Danke.
quotes.married: Admiral, you're always working so hard, aren't you. But, you shouldn't push yourself so much. I'll work with you.

quotes.fleet_join: A sortie, huh? ...Roger.
quotes.idle: Umm... is there nothing for me to do? I see... Specifically, are there no operations? Hmm...
quotes.intro: Guten tag. I am the destroyer Max Schultz, but "Max" is good enough. My regards.
quotes.marriage: So what is this important business? Eh...? This is for me? Y... you... hmm... I-I see... So that's how it is... hmm... danke schön...
quotes.married: Darling... haven't you already done more than enough? Let's slow down a bit. It'll be fine.

quotes.fleet_join: Heavy cruiser Prinz Eugen, setting off!
quotes.idle: Bismarck onee-sama... I wonder if she's okay...? I'm a little worried... maybe I should go see how she's doing?
quotes.intro: Guten morgen! I'm the heavy cruiser, Prinz Eugen. I'll be in your care!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, you said you needed something? Wha- t-this is for me? U-Umm, Bismarck onee-sama is... a-ah... u-um... da... danke! I'll treasure it!!
quotes.married: Woah...! Admiral, if you're tired, you need to take a little break. Definitely! Got it?

quotes.fleet_join: Heavy cruiser Prinz Eugen, setting off!
quotes.idle: Bismarck onee-sama... I wonder if she's okay...? I'm a little worried... maybe I should go see how she's doing?
