quotes.fleet_join: 16th Destroyer Division, Amatsukaze, setting sail!
quotes.idle: Eh? I'm... not bored or anything. Even after getting the data for the new boiler, I still have a lot more work to do. I-I really do!
quotes.intro: Is a good breeze on the way? The next-generation destroyer prototype— I, Amatsukaze, shall have my turn.
quotes.marriage: You... What... is this? You're... You're really fine with it being me? ...Thank you. I'm truly grateful. ...Eh!? For me...? Umm... I'm willing if you are, but...
quotes.married: Dear... From time to time, go take a break. Breaks are important, too... Ugh! Are you even listening!? Geez...

quotes.fleet_join: Repair ship Akashi, now departing!
quotes.idle: Right... don't worry! I'm busy with things such as repairs and procuring new machinery! So don't worry! ... really...
quotes.intro: I'm Repair ship Akashi. If you take a little damage, I can fix you up in the base. Just leave it to me!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? Ehh... for me!? No way...! I-I'll treasure it! Thank you! You want to process the ring in my factory? Geez... I wonder who the lucky person is?
quotes.married: Admiral... you've gotta make sure you fix yourself up sometimes. Just leave the maintenance... to me, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Fleet flagship Ooyodo, now sortieing.
quotes.idle: Admiral, it's time for the next mission. Ad... Admiral...? Admiral? Are you listening? Hey...
quotes.intro: Admiral, light cruiser Ooyodo has entered the line of battle. Please entrust the fleet directives and administration to me.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, did you call for me? Eh...? Is this for me? Thank you so much, Admiral. I will always cherish this.
quotes.married: Admiral, I truly cannot thank you enough... for always keeping me in your heart. I've... been watching over you all this time. Did you notice?

quotes.fleet_join: Submarine Fleet flagship, Taigei, heading out!
quotes.idle: A-D-M-I-R-A-L~ Admiral! U-um... about the submarine operations... Ah, a short break... I-I see... No, it's nothing... mmhm...
quotes.intro: Good day, I'm Submarine Tender Taigei. I may be inexperienced, but I am glad to be of service.
quotes.marriage: Admiral... I'll always be besides you... I thank you from the bottom of my heart for raising me in my default form. I will always, yes, always be thankful.
quotes.married: Aren't you a little tired, Admiral? As I am a Submarine Tender, I am quite confident in my livability.

quotes.fleet_join: Okay! Carrier Ryuuhou, casting off!
quotes.idle: A-D-M-I-R-A-L~ Admiral! Um... is Carrier Task Force deploying? Ah, a short break... I-I see, right...
quotes.intro: Carrier Ryuuhou, remodeled from a Submarine Tender. I'll once again try my best as a carrier!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... I'll always, always be part of the admiral's carrier task force! I thank you from the bottom of my heart for raising me as a remodeled carrier. I will always, yes, always be thankful.
quotes.married: Aren't you tired, Admiral? Want to take a quick nap on my flight deck? Please do!

quotes.fleet_join: Ready? Yukikaze, I'm going on ahead!
quotes.idle: Commander! Heyyy! Commaanderrr! COMMAANDERRR! HEY! Hey, can't you hear me?
quotes.intro: Kagerou-class destroyer, tenth ship. Tokitsukaze... ...has appeared.
quotes.marriage: Commander! What's up? Then, who? ...Eh? ...M-Me!? W-Why!? Well... Well... ...Thank you... ...! Are you looking for Hatsukaze? You're not? ...Amatsukaze? That's wrong, too?
quotes.married: Commander! Have you seen Yukikaze? Oh, I see... Then, you're fine, too! Hey~♪ Heey~♪

quotes.fleet_join: Repair ship Akashi, now departing!
quotes.idle: Right... don't worry! I'm busy with things such as repairs and procuring new machinery! So don't worry! ... really...
quotes.intro: Repair Ship Akashi, at your service! Leave the emergency maintenance at the base to me! I'll support the girls in the front lines!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? Ehh... for me!? No way...! I-I'll treasure it! Thank you! You want to process the ring in my factory? Geez... I wonder who the lucky person is?
quotes.married: Admiral... you've gotta make sure you fix yourself up sometimes. Just leave the maintenance... to me, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Come now! To the front!
quotes.idle: N-no! I'm not... It's not like i'm bored or anything!
quotes.intro: I am Tone! With my addition to the fleet, there will be no problems searching out the enemy!
quotes.marriage: That's right, my scouts have found the enemy fleet!! ...Eh? Enough of that? ...Then what is it? What is this?
quotes.married: Admiral, you're working hard too!

quotes.fleet_join: Chikuma, all preparations complete! Heading out!
quotes.idle: Well… It is about time to lay out an operation… Oh you seem busy… Ah…
quotes.intro: Second ship of the Tone-class, aviation-cruiser Chikuma. I'll do my best with nee-san.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, calling me out to this place... I... my heart is set on my oneesan... Eh? It's about formations? Oh my... Even me...
quotes.married: Admiral… Thanks for everything until now. You're just like Tone nee-san. Fufu...

quotes.fleet_join: I'd like to show the true power of the Carrier Ryuuhou!
quotes.idle: A-D-M-I-R-A-L~ Admiral! Um... is Carrier Task Force deploying? Ah, a short break... I-I see, right...
quotes.intro: Carrier Ryuuhou, remodeled from a Submarine Tender. I'll once again try my best as a carrier!
quotes.marriage: Admiral... I'll always, always be part of the admiral's carrier task force! I thank you from the bottom of my heart for raising me as a remodeled carrier. I will always, yes, always be thankful.
quotes.married: Aren't you tired, Admiral? Want to take a quick nap on my flight deck? Please do!

quotes.fleet_join: Heavy cruiser, Myoukou. Heading forth!
quotes.idle: The admiral seems very busy... In that case, I should do everything I can at hand, so that the admiral may call on me whenever I'm needed.
quotes.intro: Myoukou-class Heavy Cruiser, Myoukou. Let's do our best together until the end.
quotes.marriage: I greatly respect the admiral's fabulous strategy and tactics, and always shall.
quotes.married: If the admiral falls, I...please at least rest a bit when you are tired. It is Myoukou's wish.

quotes.fleet_join: Nachi's squadron! Heading out!!
quotes.idle: No, I'm not bored. In fact i'm enjoying myself looking at what you're doing.
quotes.intro: You're.. still on combat duty? Alright, this Nachi will again, go on the battlefields with you!
quotes.marriage: Hey you… Somehow… I don't hate you…. Yeah, as long as I am with you, I can promise more great victories. Definitely.
quotes.married: You, how are you doing? ...I see, it relieves me. We can sortie more together!

quotes.fleet_join: A sortie! The battleground is... Victory is calling out to me!
quotes.idle: When is the next operation!? Hey, where's the next operation going to be!? Victory is... Battle is... Conflict is calling out to me!!!
quotes.intro: Heavy cruiser Ashigara here. If there's surface combat, leave it to me! Let's seize victory together!
quotes.marriage: To have drawn out the full extent of my abilities... You are... ...I see. You're the first one to have done it!
quotes.married: Are you alright? Don't push yourself too hard, okay? Whether it's a rendezvous or a battle, the beginning is the most crucial part! Always face them in top condition!

quotes.fleet_join: Haguro of The Fifth Squadron, heading out!
quotes.idle: E, excuse me, Commander…? Haguro is waiting for you here in case of trouble...
quotes.intro: Fourth ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Haguro. Together with everyone, I will support the front lines!
quotes.marriage: After this battle is over… T-together with the commander..! Erm.. Ummm.. Errrmm…
quotes.married: Commander… I hope this war will be over and the sea will get quiet. I pray for it. Commander… you will surely…

quotes.fleet_join: Ayanami, starting sortie!
quotes.idle: Commander, thanks for always working so hard. Ayanami will support you all the way.
quotes.intro: Nice to meet you. I'm Ayanami, a special class destroyer.
quotes.marriage: Am I Ayanami doing my best? Do I help you well? ...R-really! I'm so glad to hear it!
quotes.married: Commander, Ayanami is also working hard by myself. But, if I'm with you... I'll work even harder!

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! Second Carrier Division flagship Hiryuu, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Woah~ oh, oh, oh. So these are the blueprints for the revised Hiryuu-class aircraft carriers, the Unryuu-class. They sure were planning on making a lot... Wooow... this is amazing... A-Ah, Admiral, what was that? Sorry, but I wasn't really listening!
quotes.intro: Aircraft carrier Hiryuu here. Leave the carrier battles to me. I'll show you I can counter any and all adversity!
quotes.marriage: Sometimes... I love it... That smile... Once in a while... It's okay to forget about the fighting, you know? Hey... look at me. Yeah!
quotes.married: Admiral, I appreciate the new planes, but I still prefer to fight alongside the Tomonaga Squadron. Eh? You'll grant my request? Thank you...! Ah...! I hugged you without thinking. Sorry♪

quotes.fleet_join: Second Carrier Division flagship Souryuu, setting sail!
quotes.idle: Mmm... Nothing's going on. Well, I guess that's not a bad thing. It's a little boring, though... Time to go hang out with Hiryuu... ah, Admiral! Aye! Nothing to report!
quotes.intro: I'm the aircraft carrier, Souryuu. If you're making a carrier task fleet, you can count me in.
quotes.marriage: I'm... trying my hardest, you know? Am I being helpful? Hey... Admiral, what do I mean to you?
quotes.married: Admiral, can you spare some time go into town with me? There are things I'd like to get. Ah, not at all, not at all! I'll buy them myself. Really!

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Division 18, Arare, setting sail.
quotes.idle: Commander... Things to do... No, it's all good...
quotes.intro: I'm Arare... I won't say something like "-ncha"... I certainly won't... Nice to meet you...
quotes.marriage: Ah, what's the matter, Commander? I need to get back to work... Yeah... But, I'll accept this.
quotes.married: Commander, Arare and friends… are always thankful… to you.

quotes.fleet_join: Here I go~!!!
quotes.idle: Commander! I'll be watching over you from here! Always, always, alwaaays!!
quotes.intro: Destroyer Ooshio here~! A small body with large torpedoes! Please leave it to me!
quotes.marriage: Are you familiar with the meaning behind "Ooshio"? It's when the gravitational pull of the moon brings the waves closer. You could say it's just like the two of us.
quotes.married: Commander, how've you been? Are your days fulfilling?

quotes.fleet_join: Torpedo Squadron 1, Abukuma. Flagship, front side, moving out!
quotes.idle: Geez! I thought you might have forgotten about me!
quotes.intro: My turn to shine? That's gotta be it! Abukuma, sortieing!
quotes.marriage: Admiral~, thanks for waiting! I want to say couple of words of thanks to you… because you looked after me with such care, I got a bit more confident. Admiral, thank you.
quotes.married: Admiral, please don't overdo it, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft carrier, Unryuu. I'm sortieing.
quotes.idle: Admiral? ...Admiral? Can't you hear me? Should I send a recon plane? Or maybe a dive bomber?
quotes.intro: Unryuu-class aircraft carrier, Unryuu, reporting in. Admiral, it's a pleasure to meet you.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, why are you being so formal? Why did you choose me? There are others who... No... I will treasure this. It's precious to me. ...Eh? This is for me? This is... um...
quotes.married: Admiral, even if the decisive battle is inevitable, relax your shoulders and let's try to take it easy. It'll be just fine. I will always be by your side, so...

quotes.fleet_join: Carrier Division flagship, Amagi. Starting the sortie!
quotes.idle: Hakodate...? Why is that... such a familiar name...? ...Am I imagining it? Ah! Admiral, did you call for me? I will fight on with everything I have.
quotes.intro: I'm the Unryuu-class aircraft carrier known as Amagi. Admiral, it's an honor to be working for you. I will dedicate myself to it!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, did you call for me? Always... I will cherish this forever! Eh? For me? This is...? ...I accept. Admiral, thank you so much!
quotes.married: Admiral, as always, thank you so much for your hard work. I'm right here on standby, so... please call me if you ever need anything.

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft carrier Katsuragi, preparations complete! Starting the sortie!
quotes.idle: I see, I see. So this is a Ryuusei Kai, huh? Mhm, mhm. I'd overheard people talking about it... But wait, isn't that a Reppuu? This is great! It's perfect for me! ...Eh?
quotes.intro: Unryuu-class aircraft carrier, third ship Katsuragi here! Eh? You called me a floating anti-air battery? Y-You're way off...! What are you even talking about!?
quotes.marriage: What is it, Admiral? U-Um... Thank you! I-I...! Can't you see that I'm kind of busy? I have my hands full with these engines. They need all kinds of maint- ...er...?
quotes.married: Admiral... Hey, if only these aircraft were supplied, I could... ...Eh... what? Even if you look at me with such gentle eyes, it's not... It's not getting you anywhere! Geez...
quotes.remodel: I'll give it all I've got.

quotes.fleet_join: Hatsuharu, casting off!
quotes.idle: Aah, well, you know, it would be all right if we did some work... it would be all right, you know?
quotes.intro: We are Hatsuharu. With us following, thou wilt be fine!
quotes.marriage: You...!? W-w-w-w-aaa! To expose us to such shameful words! Shame on you! For shame...
quotes.married: You should... rest a little better as well. Of course, we can rest when it's important. ...It's pleasant!

quotes.fleet_join: Yes, fifth Shiratsuyu-class Harusame... heading out!
quotes.idle: Commander? ...Um, Commander? ...I wonder if he's busy? ...Yeah, I have to do my best too!
quotes.intro: Fifth Shiratsuyu-class destroyer, Harusame, yes. Leave the transport missions to me... desu.
quotes.marriage: Commander... U-um, what is it? Is it a new transport mission? Eh, it's not? Then night battle duty? That's not it either? Eh... for me... Fufu, I'll treasure it.
quotes.married: Um, I can't really say it well, but... I'm always grateful. Truly.

quotes.fleet_join: Task Force flagship, aircraft carrier Unryuu. I'm setting sail.
quotes.idle: Admiral? ...Admiral? Can't you hear me? Should I send a recon plane? Or maybe a dive bomber?
quotes.intro: Unryuu-class aircraft carrier, Unryuu, present. Admiral, please leave the reborn Task Force to me.
quotes.marriage: Admiral, why are you being so formal? Why did you choose me? There are others who... No... I will treasure this. It's precious to me. ...Eh? This is for me? This is... um...
quotes.married: Admiral, even if the decisive battle is inevitable, relax your shoulders and let's try to take it easy. It'll be just fine. I will always be by your side, so...

quotes.fleet_join: Ushio, moving out.
quotes.idle: Admiral, um... Ushio, awaiting orders... ah... am I a burden to you...? Oh... u-um... um!
quotes.intro: I'm the Special Type Ayanami-class destroyer, Ushio. It would be nice if I could be dismissed soon...
quotes.marriage: Admiral, that is... I'll adore... no, umm... respect you! Yes! Always!
quotes.married: Admiral. Even before Shoukaku-san does, and even more kindly than Mutsu-san does, you're always there watching over me. I-I'm truly always... thank you!
quotes.remodel: I'll save everyone I possibly can!

quotes.fleet_join: Alright! The fully remodeled Junyou-san is ready to sortie! Setting sail!
quotes.idle: *sigh* Looks like downtime... Oh well, time to drink♪ Let's see... maybe I'll have some hot sake♪
quotes.intro: Merchant ship turned carrier, Junyou here~! Hyaha!
quotes.marriage: I worked really hard so I wouldn't lose to those standard carriers. You're the only admiral who really gets me, y'know what I mean? Hey... Gimme a kiss♥
quotes.married: Yo~ Admiral, you wanna have a drink with me sometime? I got some really good sake♪ Ah, don't worry. I brought some snacks, too.

quotes.fleet_join: Hayashimo, heading out.
quotes.idle: Just like this... I'm always watching. Watching... always... forever.
quotes.intro: I've... come again, to these seas. Yuugumo-class destroyer, Hayashimo... reporting for duty.
quotes.marriage: Commander, meeting you, I... I'm glad. So, just this is enough... eh? This is... truly? I... can I change, I wonder?
quotes.married: Commander. I think you're working a bit too much too. Umm... Sometimes, together, we should... Uu... I-it's nothing... Uu...

quotes.fleet_join: Yeah. Leave it to Kiyoshimo!
quotes.idle: Hey, Commander? What's that, what are you doing? Hey, watcha dooin? Tell me tell me tell meeeeeee?
quotes.intro: Hello! Last of the Yuugumo-class, it's Kiyoshimo! I'm a bit late, but I'll be in your care!
quotes.marriage: Commander? What's wrong, you have such a serious look on your face? Eh, what's... this? This is for me? Really? Nn... thank you. I wonder... why... I'm starting to tear up.
quotes.married: Commander? You know, if you're tired, you can take a break with me? Right, right?

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Fusou, setting sail.
quotes.idle: Um... Admiral? I wonder if I wasn't heard... Admiral? Admiraal? ...Oh my, that's a relief. Fusou, waiting here on stand by.
quotes.intro: Of the two Fusou-class super-dreadnought battleships, I am the elder sister, Fusou. Please take care of me and my younger sister Yamashiro.
quotes.marriage: My main cannons, aren't they wonderful? But specialising in firepower too much can lead to all kinds of problems... If it's Admiral, I'm sure you understand, right?
quotes.married: Admiral… If you work too hard, your body will get bad. Oh, me?...I...*sigh*

quotes.fleet_join: Fusou-class battleship Yamashiro, sortieing!
quotes.idle: What...? You're saying Nee-sama and I can't go out to that part of the ocean anymore...? What do you mean by that? How dreadful... from the very start...!
quotes.intro: Of the two Fusou-class battleships, I am the younger sister, Yamashiro. Umm... have you seen Fusou nee-sama?
quotes.marriage: Th... ...Thank you. ...But... My heart shall always be with Fusou nee-sama's... I'm sorry.
quotes.married: ....Admiral. Just like Nee-sama, I think... you are a good person. I'll always... be grateful for everything... I mean it, you know?

quotes.fleet_join: DesDiv 9 moving out. You heard that, Yamagumo? Follow me!
quotes.idle: Wh-What? There's nothing for me to do? Well, it's fine, but kinda annoying. I know, shall I massage your shoulders? Ah, I'm kidding. Just kidding, of course!
quotes.intro: Asashio-class destroyer, Asagumo, reporting in! So you're the commander... huh. Hmm. Well, it's fine. I'll do it!
quotes.marriage: What, Commander? I'm pretty busy here... Heh, what? Another joke. ...Eh, you're serious? Ah, what do I do... Y-Yamagumo is... Ehh, umm...
quotes.married: Commander...Its good that you're working hard, but if you overdo things, it makes me worried, seriously! Yes, make sure you rest appropriately...got it?
quotes.remodel: I'll take it off your hands!

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Yamagumo~ setting sa~il.
quotes.idle: U~m~ Yamagumo kind of likes having free time~ But Asagumo-nee~ she's an impatient person~ you know~?
quotes.intro: Good morning~~ Asashio Destroyer number six, Yamagumo. Please treat me well!
quotes.marriage: Commander, what is it? Are you giving this box to Yamagumo? I wonder what it is? Ooh, pretty~ Thank you~
quotes.married: Commander, you're working so hard~ How admirable~ Yamagumo thinks that you're really quite amazing~ Yes, really!

quotes.fleet_join: Destroyer Nowaki, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Maikaze, what are you up to...? Are you well...? Ah, Commander! I'm alright! Nowaki, on standby!
quotes.intro: Kagerou-class Destroyer, Nowaki, reporting in. Well, Commander. Let us proceed.

quotes.marriage: Admiral, did...did you call me? Am I being reclassified? Don't tell me, I'm being struck from the registry? Uh, uhm... what? Eh, this...is for me? Really? Uh, uhm, uhmmm, I...
quotes.married: Admiral- ah, uhm, I mean, Admiral-san? Shall I bring some tea?

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft carrier Saratoga, setting sail. Follow me.
quotes.idle: Yup! With this, the planes won't have any issues! There's quite a lot of them, so this is pretty tough. Oh, Nagato! Hi! Eh...? You're going to do exercises now? Sorry about this, but I have other duties to perform for today. Maybe next time!
quotes.intro: Hello~! Aircraft carrier Saratoga here. I've been improved, with an enhanced rigging and planes! Let's do our best together from now on!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, how are you doing? Oh my god...! It's beautiful! Eh? This is for me... you mean? Ah...! Is it okay if I open it?

quotes.fleet_join: Battleship Musashi, moving out now!
quotes.idle: If you're not too busy, how about going outside for a short break, partner? That's something a model admiral should do too. What? You're laying out future strategies? I had not considered that, partner, forgive me.
quotes.intro: Hmph, I've been waiting, partner... Ah, very well. 2nd of the Yamato-class and a Kai Yamato-class battleship, Musashi, has arrived!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, I have confidence that I will guard you from any adversaries. You sure had me taken lightly. With that said, I'll be counting on you from now on, partner. Hmph... You doubt me?
quotes.married: I know you have your own troubles, partner. Yeah, I understand. However, you don't have to worry, for I am around.

quotes.fleet_join: Fifth Fleet, Tama, sortieing, nya.

quotes.marriage: Commander, why are you looking at me like that? Hweh~~! I'm a... a little nervous...!
quotes.married: Commander, this is embarrassing...! Please don't... gaze at me like that...

quotes.intro: Hi! I'm the 5th ship of the Essex-class carriers, Intrepid! So you're the Admiral then? Wonderful! Now then, let's get going! That's fine, right?
quotes.marriage: How's being a Sea, Air & Space Museum? Well, I've been used for films, for anti-terrorism... Eh? That's not what you're here to talk about? Is this, for me? I'm opening it! Ah! Eh? Is this, for real? No way! Thank you for everything, Honey!
quotes.married: Honey, what are you doing? Preparations for tomorrow's operations? Jeez, isn't that enough for now! Come on, look, look! Don't I look wonderful like this? Peace is great, isn't it?
quotes.remodel: Wonderful. I wish everyone could see~

quotes.fleet_join: Aircraft carrier Saratoga, setting sail. Follow me.
quotes.idle: Yup! With this, the planes won't have any issues! There's quite a lot of them, so this is pretty tough. Oh, Nagato! Hi! Eh...? You're going to do exercises now? Sorry about this, but I have other duties to perform for today. Maybe next time!
quotes.intro: Hello~! Aircraft carrier Saratoga here. I've been improved, with an enhanced rigging and planes! Let's do our best together from now on!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, how are you doing? Oh my god...! It's beautiful! Eh? This is for me... you mean? Ah...! Is it okay if I open it?
quotes.married: Admiral? Are you feeling worn out? I can go make you tea or anything else that will get you going again. Eh? Bread? I'm not so good at making that... although on the other hand, I am pretty good at making cakes. I'll bake one for you. Please wait a bit, okay?

quotes.fleet_join: 1st Surface Escort Division, Hiburi, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Admiral, umm, the code for the Hi-convoy is... Ah, that's right. I got it. What should I do? Should I reply?
quotes.intro: 1st ship of the Hiburi-class Kaiboukan, Hiburi. The Hiburi-class is reporting for duty, Admiral. We'll do our best!
quotes.marriage: Did you call me, Admiral? I'm here now. Ah, what is... this? Can I open it now? Eh? Do it... later? Roger that... Is this the usual reward? Eh? I'm happy. I'm very grateful for it. Now then!
quotes.married: Is there anything for me to do, Admiral? An escort? An ASW sweep? Ah, I know! I'll make some tea first, alright? Please wait!
quotes.remodel: No trace... of enemy subs! Alright!

quotes.fleet_join: 1st Surface Escort Division, Daitou, sortieing now! Follow me!
quotes.idle: Hmm? Ah, a minesweeping story? Fine, I don't mind. It was an important mission back then, just like it is today. I wanted to pass a clean sea down to future generations. Hmm? Oi~, are you listening!?
quotes.intro: I'm the 2nd ship of the Hiburi-class Kaiboukan, Daitou! Reporting for duty! So you're the Admiral. Hehe~! Great! Take care of me too. Now, let's get going!
quotes.marriage: Huh, did you call me? You didn't? I see... What, if you have something to say, say it! Eh, what was that? Say it again, hey! One more time!
quotes.married: What, I don't really need to be babied. Ah... Oh... It's fine, I'm feeling fine.... Ehehe, you're nice.

quotes.fleet_join: Yes, I'll definitely be coming along too!
quotes.idle: Coastal patrol and transport fleet escort are both important things aren't they....Hey, Admiral, let's go do some work..
quotes.intro: I'm Zuihou! I've gotten my major remodel! I'll do my very, very best!
quotes.marriage: Admiral, what is it? Eh? A bouquet...? Eh? For me!? Ah, ah, what should I do… Th-Th-Thank… you. Is it an air group inspection… it's not? Ah, your face is all serious…
quotes.married: Admiral? Umm... I, think made too much tamagoyaki... will you eat it? Aah, really? Ehehe... I'm glad.
quotes.remodel: My bento, will you eat it?

quotes.fleet_join: Leave it 'ta me!
quotes.idle: Mmmmm, I'd like to go out soon.
quotes.intro: I'm a remodelled Kagerou-class now. You listenin', Admiral? Yup, it's great. Take care of me today, too.
quotes.marriage: Whenever I see Admiral doing his best all day long, somehow I just can't leave you alone... yeah! Don't be too reckless, alright!
quotes.married: Wanna go for a stroll wit me, Admiral? Hmmm? Heh~ Well?

quotes.fleet_join: 17th Destroyer, Isokaze, arriving.
quotes.idle: Commander...The 17th Destroyer Division, can sortie at any time... Hamakaze and I are ready... right Hamakaze?
quotes.intro: 12th Kagerou-class destroyer, Isokaze. Commander, let's proceed together. You do not need to worry.
quotes.marriage: Commander, what? This important discussion. Is it about the 17th Destroyer Division's formation? What, it's not? Then is it something about that Hamakaze? It has nothing to do with Hamakaze... I see. Nn... That ring... to me... w-what... eh! U-um...
quotes.married: Admiral, have you been eating well? If you don't eat and an emergency occurs, you may not survive it. Even surviving is a splendid battle in itself. So, let's go to Mamiya to eat.

quotes.fleet_join: Hamakaze of the 17th Destroyer Division, sortieing!
quotes.idle: Umm... excuse me! Is it time... for the next battle yet?
quotes.intro: I'm Hamakaze. The combat potential of DesDiv17 has increased. We're sure to win now.
quotes.marriage: Admiral. If it's about matchmaking, don't you think there are plenty of other girls you can ask who are more into that? ...Eh? Me? N-No! I... this sort of thing... b-but, I'll face it head-on, study it, and put all of my effort into it... okay...?
quotes.married: Is anything wrong? Are you feeling tired? Mm, shall I prepare something nutritious for you? Will you eat it?

quotes.fleet_join: Yes, I'll definitely be coming along too!
quotes.idle: Coastal patrol and transport fleet escort are both important things aren't they....Hey, Admiral, let's go do some work..
quotes.intro: I'm Zuihou! I've gotten my major remodel! I'll do my very, very best!

quotes.married: Admiral? Umm... I, think made too much tamagoyaki... will you eat it? Aah, really? Ehehe... I'm glad.
quotes.remodel: My bento, will you eat it?

quotes.fleet_join: Samuel B. Roberts, heading out! Now then, let's hang in there with the escorting today too!
quotes.idle: Oh, hi, Gambier Bay! What's the matter? Ah, that? If you want to do that, then do it here like this, and done! Huh? Alright, I guess I'll have to come with you. You sure need help a lot. Not that I mind!
quotes.intro: I'm John C. Butler-class destroyer escort Samuel B. Roberts! Make sure to remember it! Ah, too long? Then "Sam" is fine, okay? Nice to meet you!
quotes.marriage: Huh? What, enemies!? W-Where? Oh, it's you? You really surprised me! What's the matter, Admiral? Oh, me? Yeah, I'm fine... you're being weird. You're giving this? Later? Ohh? Later is fine. I think? Ehehe. Thanks a lot!
quotes.married: Hmm? Are you tired? Ah, okay, then... would gum be good? Okay! Oh, you don't need it? What? What's wrong? Okay, could you lie down for a sec? Theeere!

quotes.fleet_join: 2nd Surface Escort Division, Fukae, sortieing! I'll protect everyone.

quotes.remodel: I think this will do. It should work.

quotes.marriage: Ah, Commander! Great work!... Erm, right.. Um, here's a Hawaiian souvenir chocolate for you!
quotes.married: Commander... You've really been doing your best, haven't you? Yeah. I have do my best too, alongside you.

quotes.fleet_join: 2nd ship of the Remodelled Kagerou-class, Shiranui, deploying!
quotes.idle: Shiranui is absolutely not bored. No, please don't mind me. Do as you like...
quotes.intro: I'm the upgraded Shiranui. I'm counting on your continued guidance and encouragement.
quotes.marriage: Commander, what do you think of my battles...? Oh, I see... Well, that's fine too.
quotes.married: Is there something on Shiranui's face? ...I see, then... it's fine. No, it's nothing... Something wrong?

quotes.fleet_join: I'll definitely be the one to finish them off! Setting sail!

quotes.fleet_join: Hatsuyuki, sortieing...

quotes.marriage: Erm, umm… I like the commander!.. What is it? Don't look at me with that face!

quotes.marriage: I just wanted to tell you... Well, I don't really dislike you, you know. I guess... you can order me to do anything... you want... What are you...!? I-I didn't mean it like that!

quotes.fleet_join: Headin' out!

quotes.marriage: Umm…. Admiral… do you have a girlfriend?.... Oh, so that's it. Fufu, hmm~ I see~♪
quotes.married: I'm very happy.

quotes.marriage: Am I Ayanami doing my best? Do I help you well? ...R-really! I'm so glad to hear it!

quotes.fleet_join: Well, let go~! It's time for sortie!
quotes.idle: Hurn, person like Shikinami will be forgotten anyway... Well, that's fine... that's not fine...

quotes.married: Commander… It's not good to work so hard. … Hey, take your time!

quotes.marriage: Admiral... Even though it's the time and place... If you forget the mood and timing, it'll be a "no", you know?

quotes.fleet_join: Off I go! With all my spirit! Held high!

quotes.marriage: Thank you for your favour, Commander... O-oh.. I see... I-I'm so embarrassed~! B-but... My heart... belongs to oneesama. Eh? It's not that kind of talk!?
quotes.married: Hiei can still fight some more. Commander, let's do our best together!

quotes.fleet_join: Haruna... is now... starting the sortie!

quotes.marriage: Having favour from the admiral is nice. B~ut, if I'm all friendly with the admiral, Tenryuu-chan will be all alone, you know~. I'm sorry, okay~?

quotes.fleet_join: Kuma! Sortieing, kuma!

quotes.intro: Kuma~ Nice to meet you, kuma.
quotes.marriage: Fufufu~ I've caught the admiral, kuma. I'm not gonna let you go, kuma. Kumakuma~!

quotes.fleet_join: Tama, sortieing nya!
quotes.idle: Nya, Nya~! Nya... Nya!

quotes.marriage: Admiral, please stop calling me with chan at the end, nya. It sort of... feels different, nya.
quotes.married: Thanks for the hard work, nya. Take a break with Tama, nya. Nyaa~

quotes.marriage: Don't mind me sayin' it, but your orders in battle send shivers through my spine. You're not half bad!
quotes.married: So it goes.

quotes.fleet_join: It's time! Leave it to me!
quotes.idle: Alright...! I ran all day again today! I'll run even more tomorrow! Ah! Commander! Heading out? Going for a long run? I'll come with you! Eh, you're not?
quotes.intro: Light Cruiser Nagara! Please take good care of me!
quotes.marriage: Thank you for always leading us to victory! Nagara also loves the commander!
quotes.married: Yay!

quotes.married: Admiral, it's definitely my single mounted guns, right? Right? Eh, what's that? You like my... hair too? Th-thanks... Umm... I, like you, too.

quotes.fleet_join: You called for me... Eh!? Sortie!?
quotes.idle: Admiral, you seem so busy... While you do that, I can organize your things for you. Umm... this is... it goes here... This is... here... And then! This is... huh? Th-This is... umm...

quotes.marriage: Thank you for all the support! I'm gonna work really, really hard for the admiral! Kira~n☆

quotes.idle: Shiranui is absolutely not bored. No, please don't mind me. Do as you like...

quotes.idle: Hmm...? Oh... I'm just chatting with Rensouhou-chan now... 'cause I'm really bored.
